{
  "stem": "10745.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the last place, we couldn't dig too far because it was a low land.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was water coming in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we-- the only thing was to stand up, if you could see, somebody could see from far away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See your head or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We could not allow   to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to go bending down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had to crawl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the other forest, we dug underground.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were under.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just took-- just a few branches over it or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this was a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Under there, in the low lands, we were already more-- Describe what it was like to be in these bunkers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To be in the bunker?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's not to describe, because it's a survival.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's-- like you would say a dog's life, a dog has a good life here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "An animal?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because they were killing us more than animals.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just lay down, put a little bit of leaves, and just lay on-- on the ground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's nothing I could say that-- what happened there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was all kinds of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was couples.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was the different people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They dug out a little hole, and they lived together there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so me, and my mother, and my brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were in our one hole, just the three of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If we felt that somebody knows about it or anything like that-- like we stayed in the bushes, in the one time before.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Ukrainians were going to make some vodka from the rye, or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we heard if somebody was coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they came to one-- one there, and they killed them all.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We heard that that was killed somebody, we rushed to another place.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
